{"tid":2282903,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"暫時不參與活動！MAMAMOO輝人突然身體不適送醫檢查中，行程緊急喊卡！","createTime":"2020-11-12T07:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T12:08:50.000Z","uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0205afadd52f125bd137a4c6a33debd21d33a626","tid":2282903,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_1ca644442c939b46dd952c9044d13213/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-12/131588-884410.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_1ca644442c939b46dd952c9044d13213%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-12%2F131588-884410.jpg&h=84522122&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望輝人可以早日恢復健康，跟團員們一起回到舞台上QQ<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMAMAMOO的經紀公司RBW在今天透過官咖向粉絲們表示「成員輝人11號下午在進行日程中，突然感到頸部和背部的肌肉疼痛，所以正在醫院檢查中。」，讓粉絲們都感到非常擔心～<br />\n<br />\n而MAMAMOO因為今天有MBC的FM4U《 金信英的正午希望曲》的行程，但是輝人無法參與，所以特別跟粉絲解釋缺席的原因。<br />\n<br />\n另外所屬公司也表示因為目前還在檢查中，所以之後的治療與修養將會依照輝人的復原情況，再做判斷是否回歸宣傳期的活動參與，會再透過消息告訴大家，也請粉絲們諒解。<br />\n<br />\n雖然目前無法確定病因和復原期需要多長的時間，但是都希望輝人可以好好的養傷，恢復健康才能盡快回到最愛的舞台上！<br />\n<br />\n(圖片或影片來源：IG@whee_inthemood、IG@mamamoo_official)"},{"pid":"a300e68e354cdabb3a8ef37ce74f27ed3ebeed7f","tid":2282903,"uid":255310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:37:53.000Z","msg":"快啲好返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505dafc118cb47991cb2cde6a1bf1f9b2c40a47f","tid":2282903,"uid":21234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />早日康復呀輝仔"},{"pid":"1ffc63ca754ff5c6f55e70eb8aceb98fe3ed9050","tid":2282903,"uid":368098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:44:44.000Z","msg":"Get well soon<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif